Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.65,0:00:04.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,甲胄是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.72,0:00:09.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上的时候 伤口就像假的一样不痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:13.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.97,0:00:16.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,疼痛都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:18.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:22.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这股在体内沸腾的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:28.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体中有什么狂暴的东西涌现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:30.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,献 上 身 体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:31.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是 的这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:33.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,献 上 血 肉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:35.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,献上一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:37.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:38.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,献 上 骨 髓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:41.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,献上你的一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.42,0:00:44.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,献 上 生 命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:48.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,甲胄的形状在...
Comment: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.15,DefaultSub,,0,0,0,,/------START-------/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:28.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:31.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的真正实力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:34.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这样才有粉碎的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:44.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的庞大身体打飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:50.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,何等的蛮力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:54.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是刚才那个男人的攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:02.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然弄碎了我这连炮弹都能挡住的盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:07.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个手舞大剑身穿甲胄的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:11.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是人类可以做出的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:23.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙义肢上装着大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:26.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一直就像怪物一样强悍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但今天感觉不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:32.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那只假手是大炮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:33.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:37.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有危险 如果继续那样的战斗下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:39.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才开始你是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:43.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的格斯先生伤口并未愈合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:46.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只是感觉不到伤口的疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:47.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,疼痛?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:51.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是矮人制作成的咒物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,狂战士的甲胄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:57.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,狂战士的 甲胄?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.74,0:04:03.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上那副甲胄后 再与寄宿其中的不祥之气同步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:04.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就会如同鬼神一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:09.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被强烈的感情控制 忘记痛苦和恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:13.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人类为了不让自己的肉体受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,会无意识地设定力量的上限
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:21.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,疼痛 是防止自己的肉体受伤的警报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:26.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,失去痛感的人 会发挥出不得了的力量和速度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:29.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然后超出人体的极限
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:31.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,陷入生命的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.78,0:04:40.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊 格斯他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:44.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 气的活动太剧烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:46.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我的念话无法传达过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:49.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是黑色剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:51.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我等的宿敌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:54.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那么以我这会心一击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.84,0:04:57.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:00.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:09.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:10.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:17.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:20.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这次单挑是你胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看来传言不假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:26.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你是远超其上的超级战士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:31.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 从现在开始我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,乃是为了吾主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:36.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,作光之鹰的使徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:38.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,当你的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:46.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,龙?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:53.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,使用使徒被授予的力量 埋葬黑色剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:57.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正面打中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.26,0:05:58.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:01.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能 竟然挡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:05.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人类把使徒的攻击...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:08.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不承认
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:20.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,比钢铁还坚硬的我的钢王的皮肤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:22.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,龟裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:24.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:37.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 刚才手脚转向相反的方向了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:40.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是甲胄的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:43.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,甲胄在补给折断的手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:45.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,贯穿血肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:46.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂食骨髓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:50.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,听说以前那副甲胄的持有者就像那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:52.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,整个身体被甲胄的铁齿蚕食
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:56.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,直到全身的骨头碎裂 全身的血液喷干还仍然战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:58.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,最后断气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:02.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么把那么危险的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:04.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,给濒死的格斯穿上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:08.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为 为了让同伴活下去 总要有牺栍嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:13.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 因为我的错 又要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:17.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅大人 为什么 为什么把那种东西...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:20.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:22.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你去做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:26.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是只有你这个魔法师才能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:28.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:31.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我还不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:34.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,内心又混乱 魔术会...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:39.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,清楚自身的稚嫩 知晓沉溺于力量的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:42.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此 现在的你才能够做到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:46.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那身处力量的乱流中的剑士先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:49.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你要向他展现道路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:52.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 做怎么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:54.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,去把格斯先生带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:57.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:07:59.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,试试看吧 师傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:01.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托是 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:04.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:07.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:11.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然第二次挡住了我这样形态发出的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:14.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还让我受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:16.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:18.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,火龙大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:20.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们也加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:23.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,去找魔女的人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:26.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也不能闲着不做事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好像你也很棘手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:30.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:35.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对使徒来说 单挑根本就无所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:40.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在变身的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:44.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:48.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个触感 有四五根肋骨断了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:09:00.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗方式渐渐不像人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:02.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:05.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对 那简直就像...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:11.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这边有好像很好吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.47,0:09:14.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,万一有什么不测
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就抱上史尔基逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:17.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史尔基
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:20.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:29.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是寄生在甲胄上的憎恶的乱流
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:31.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,来得及吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被这种东西吞食的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:36.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,普通人的自我会支离破碎的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:50.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生的憎恶 增幅甲胄的气但不是憎恶的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:52.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生就在这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:58.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我能办到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:02.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,从这么巨大的乱流中把人救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:05.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要是失手我也会被这乱流吞没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是犹豫的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:22.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,光之泡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生记忆的片段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:33.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好像灯火一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.58,0:10:36.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,成群的暗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:45.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 什么啊 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:47.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卷进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:49.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:00.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:02.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅大人的...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:19.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 这是格斯先生的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:23.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅大人的护符防止了自我的崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:29.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 不能随波逐流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,随波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:35.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对 你会因为你而消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:38.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,会被这片领域拉进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:40.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:41.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,自己是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:44.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,I K Σ  Λ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fsp-42\pos(995,1015)}ии
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:49.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,HБАЯьыъц
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:52.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,使徒 敌人 朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:53.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格里菲斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:55.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:57.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能怎样都可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:11:59.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:01.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你旅行的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.85,0:12:03.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正在战斗的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为了怎样都可以的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:10.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人类的灵魂是不会如此破烂不堪的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:11.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:12.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:14.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:23.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:30.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是 谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:38.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:43.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 不要碰她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:47.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,回忆起来她的名字是卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喀丝 卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:53.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字是 格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:56.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是烙印的剑士 格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:01.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是保护烙印的女子卡思嘉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:08.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,承受我的灼热吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:14.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:22.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:23.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:25.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:39.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:51.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好惨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:03.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:05.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:11.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:27.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而且好年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:30.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,做得不错 史尔基
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:36.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这片森林也撑不了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:41.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,灵树烧毁的话这岸领域也就会关闭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:45.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:50.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是古老东西飘荡的时间的狭间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:54.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我和这棵树的寿命也太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:58.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算阳光再如何舒适
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:02.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,新的东西也不能永远停留在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:05.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,离巢的时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:11.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,离开这里 找到自己的道路吧 我得意的弟子哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:15.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和你相处的时间虽然短暂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:21.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但却是我一生中最为安逸的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:23.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:25.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:27.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:30.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:33.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 黑色剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:37.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:41.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,身为火龙的我也无法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:44.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,生命只是变了形式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:48.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在你梦中再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:53.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能否抓住眼前的命运就靠你自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:58.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福你的成长 我亲爱的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:04.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了 我的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:26.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:36.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是抵抗组织的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:38.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:45.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是米特兰军阿古罗骑士团团长拉班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:48.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 拉班大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:52.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,团长竟然亲自前来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:58.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,们至今的所作所为 作为武人深感敬佩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:04.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 抵抗组织只是空有其名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:09.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在暗地里仓皇逃命已经很吃力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:13.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在温达姆城
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:16.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很难想像还是现世 已经化为魔都了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:19.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,抵抗者全部处死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:23.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被抓住的人 不论身份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:26.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,都当成战奴送上战场了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:29.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,女人们被关在城堡里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:33.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被用于库夏人的奇怪仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:35.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,生死不明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:39.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下老弱病残了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:43.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,何等可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:46.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还有一线希望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:50.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,夏洛特公主还健在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:55.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聪说被关在那个再生之塔的顶层了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:58.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,此话当真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:17:59.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,千真万确
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:04.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为了得到这条情报 我们失去了很多的同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:06.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,公主大人没事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:10.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,皇家的血脉没有断就有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:18.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拉班大人 我们被困在都城不知道外界的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:22.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想确认一个传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:25.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鹰 在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:28.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙 是他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:37.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拉班大人 这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:44.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个怪物究竟是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:46.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,库夏人的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:53.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,库夏人用魔法控制那些半人半兽的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:00.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:03.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说刚亲眼得见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:09.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何时城市被大雾笼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:16.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好像被雾召唤而来 怪物们开始在街上横行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.74,0:19:21.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,市民们深感恐惧 都躲在屋里不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:36.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:46.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,箭? 从哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:52.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:06.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,温达姆的市民们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:08.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在暂且躲起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:14.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天卷走城中瘴气的强风会吹起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:18.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:22.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还身负任务 就此告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:24.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,躲藏忍耐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:27.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等到鹰带来风暴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.00,0:22:10.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.46,0:22:14.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:17.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是小孩啊 不过就是一个大水坑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.80,0:22:19.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 史尔基
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:33.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.53,0:22:42.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:45.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.83,0:22:52.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体可没有那么纤弱 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:58.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还是把那身甲胄脱下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.59,0:23:01.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,起码静养四五天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:04.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,本来我就差不多睡了一个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:06.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再磨蹭下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.89,0:23:10.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说不想战斗的时候那样完全感不到疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:13.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是多亏它旅行才能继续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:15.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.27,0:23:16.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是被诅咒的铠甲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.86,0:23:19.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,再战斗的话不知何时又会失控
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.65,0:23:22.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到那时候 不是还有一个可靠的魔法师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.28,0:23:26.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都是精灵 现在就一起黏黏糊糊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.70,0:23:28.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.66,0:23:31.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要是再发生那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.46,0:23:35.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就算现在不能保证性命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.08,0:23:38.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.63,0:23:46.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为再也见不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.39,0:23:52.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在阳光下 如此的闲逸
Comment: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:33.47,EDChs,,0,0,0,,/--------ED---------/
